  "detailed_description": "Tower To Heaven is a simple, fun and pretty JRPG with a casual mode and dice-rolling speed-run mode.<br><br>With easy controls and an easily attainable finish, you will battle through 100 or 1000 levels in casual or speed-run mode. Find the special levels while you search for something to wash those doughnuts down with.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759580/extras/53d0b0e49a24a135bbb2ea36279cd287.poster.avif?t=1667921130\" width=64 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759580/extras/53d0b0e49a24a135bbb2ea36279cd287.webm?t=1667921130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple battles<br></li><li>Collect doughnuts<br></li><li>100 or 1000 levels<br></li><li>Find the special levels<br></li><li>Roll 666 for instawin!</li></ul>",
